snippet.textDisplay: Imagine rival gangs coexisting as brothers, that’s what I witnessed in this video. They weren’t gang members sitting up there, but more like a family. If they can come together on this show and have a civil and meaningful conversation, then I I’m positive they can do it in the outside world. It’s down right meaningless to take lives and hurt each other for the name of your gang, because in the end heaven and hell don’t discriminate and everyone will have to coexist then. Yes, the rivalry of gangs dates back long ago and started for particular reasons however, although the past can’t be erased, the future can always be changed for the better.
